WEBVTT

01:18.687 --> 01:20.341
Automated voice:
<i>Rejuvenation commenced.</i>

01:22.386 --> 01:24.171
<i>Compression suits activated.</i>

01:31.830 --> 01:34.050
There'’s been a breach.
We gotta get everyone
out of the bay.

01:34.050 --> 01:35.573
- What happened?
- Hell if I know.

01:45.583 --> 01:48.064
Go, go, go, go.
Go, go, go, go.

02:03.645 --> 02:05.125
Oh, Susan! Susan, no!

02:13.089 --> 02:16.223
The room is collapsing!
Go, go!

02:16.223 --> 02:19.226
Everybody, get in!
Get in there!

02:19.226 --> 02:21.315
Secure your helmets
until we stabilize!

02:21.315 --> 02:23.230
- Come on, move! Move!
- Get in there!

02:23.230 --> 02:24.709
Get your helmets!

02:32.282 --> 02:35.503
Secure your helmets
until we stabilize!

02:43.772 --> 02:45.861
Trent! Trent, come on,
we have to go!

02:45.861 --> 02:47.254
The bay'’s imploding.
We have to go.

02:47.254 --> 02:49.038
- No! Please, I gotta try!
- Trent.

03:10.581 --> 03:12.279
- Come on.
- No!

03:12.279 --> 03:13.497
No.

03:45.355 --> 03:46.748
Oh, no.

05:29.633 --> 05:31.069
Where the hell are we going?

05:31.069 --> 05:32.636
We need to speak
to our commanding officers,

05:32.636 --> 05:34.290
- find out what just happened.
- Whoa, whoa, wait.

05:34.290 --> 05:36.074
We'’re going to the commanding
officers'’ cryo bay?

05:36.074 --> 05:37.685
I'’m not waking up
