05:37.685 --> 05:40.122
I think this more than qualifies
as sufficient emergency.

05:42.429 --> 05:45.519
Seriously?

05:45.519 --> 05:46.694
Fine, I'’ll wake her up.

06:08.716 --> 06:10.892
When in God'’s name will someone
tell us what happened?

06:10.892 --> 06:12.676
I heard a fuel tank exploded.

06:12.676 --> 06:14.678
Yeah, I heard
we hit an asteroid.

06:14.678 --> 06:16.985
But I'’d like someone
from command to brief us.

06:16.985 --> 06:19.944
Please do not spread
unsubstantiated rumors.

06:19.944 --> 06:21.468
I'’m sure we will know
when they know.

06:21.468 --> 06:25.297
Until then,
