06:25.297 --> 06:27.517
Excuse me.
Is this Med Bay 12?

06:27.517 --> 06:29.911
- I was messaged to report to--
- Group 3, you'’re late.

06:29.911 --> 06:31.129
Get on the table over there

06:31.129 --> 06:32.479
