your compression suit.

06:36.874 --> 06:39.529
I said table first,
then suit.

06:39.529 --> 06:42.097
- My legs!
- You'’ve been in
a cryogenic state

06:42.097 --> 06:44.708
for a long time.

06:44.708 --> 06:46.710
A certain amount
of muscle atrophy occurs

06:46.710 --> 06:48.190
even while wearing the suit.

06:48.190 --> 06:49.931
Will I ever get my legs back?

06:49.931 --> 06:53.587
My God, man,
did you pay no attention
during orientation?

06:53.587 --> 06:56.154
There was a lot to take in.

06:56.154 --> 06:58.505
You'’ll be out of your suit
and on your feet soon

06:58.505 --> 07:00.332
