your rehab appointments.

07:00.332 --> 07:02.944
- Okay.
- On time.

07:02.944 --> 07:05.990
James Brice?
Is there a Lieutenant
James Brice in here?

07:07.339 --> 07:08.993
Aye.

07:11.561 --> 07:13.955
You'’re wanted on Cent-Com, stat.

07:13.955 --> 07:16.479
Well, I'’m assigned
to navigation.

07:16.479 --> 07:19.177
I haven'’t worked Cent-Com
since I was a wee lad.

07:19.177 --> 07:22.267
- Today you work Cent-Com.
- Aye, aye, Captain.

07:22.267 --> 07:24.313
Lieutenant, just like you.

07:24.313 --> 07:26.315
Lieutenant?

07:38.240 --> 07:40.547
So how can I help you,
Lieutenant?

07:40.547 --> 07:42.505
We can'’t access the flight log
and cam recordings.

07:42.505 --> 07:44.420
We need to know what happened,
what our status is,

07:44.420 --> 07:46.596
- but we'’re locked out.
- Look, I'’ll be honest.

07:46.596 --> 07:49.425
I don'’t even know
