be doing this?

07:50.557 --> 07:52.428
He practically lives
for this shit.

07:55.170 --> 07:57.999
Mayweather is dead,
along with everyone else

07:57.999 --> 07:59.609
in the commanding
officers'’ cryo bay.

08:14.450 --> 08:17.148
That must be the last load.
I have no charges left.

08:18.933 --> 08:20.761
Any word from command
