08:38.169 --> 08:40.128
I'’m Serbian, you moron.

08:42.434 --> 08:43.827
You certainly are.

08:47.135 --> 08:49.137
I was so worried I lost you.

08:49.137 --> 08:50.573
You wanna put us in trouble?

08:50.573 --> 08:52.488
I didn'’t know
what was happening,

08:52.488 --> 08:54.272
where you were,
or even if you were alive.

08:54.272 --> 08:56.405
If someone was to see us,
