10:20.184 --> 10:23.231
But getting to learn
from Major Andrews?

10:23.231 --> 10:26.974
That'’s a dream of mine.
He'’s a legendary horticulturist.

10:26.974 --> 10:29.977
- Okay, listen up.
- I'’m not gonna beat
around the bush.

10:29.977 --> 10:31.587
We'’ve all been
in cryogenic sleep

10:31.587 --> 10:33.720
for exactly
five years and 92 days,

10:33.720 --> 10:36.766
which means
once we get back to speed,

10:36.766 --> 10:39.726
we still have over a year to go
before reaching Proxima B.

10:39.726 --> 10:41.945
No one told us
what happened to the ship.

10:44.731 --> 10:47.734
- We don'’t know.
- What do you mean
you don'’t know?

10:47.734 --> 10:49.170
It could'’ve been an asteroid,
