11:19.591 --> 11:21.071
can be retrofitted to work here
on the ship.

11:21.071 --> 11:22.986
We just have to repurpose it.

11:22.986 --> 11:25.423
Until then,
we are on tight rations.

11:25.423 --> 11:28.775
This means no showers,
laundry, or any unnecessary
water uses.

11:28.775 --> 11:33.518
What if we'’re not able
to repurpose it?

11:33.518 --> 11:35.433
Even with rationing,
