11:55.453 --> 11:57.238
We had been carrying
a year'’s supply,

11:57.238 --> 11:58.935
but that was held
in the storage units we lost.

12:00.807 --> 12:02.678
This ship has an additional
six weeks of food,

12:02.678 --> 12:05.855
but we will need
to reserve some of that
for post arrival.

12:05.855 --> 12:08.945
You expect to ration six weeks
of food for over a year?

12:08.945 --> 12:11.687
Okay, I demand to hear
from Captain Lester.

12:11.687 --> 12:14.081
- Where'’s the Captain?
- She'’s dead.

12:19.434 --> 12:21.044
What about Stuber?

12:22.742 --> 12:25.701
