12:25.701 --> 12:27.355
We lost them all
in the incident.

12:31.185 --> 12:34.188
The entire high command,
the mentor class,

12:34.188 --> 12:38.018
our top engineers, scientists,
architects, teachers,

12:38.018 --> 12:40.281
everybody that was in charge
of running this ship

12:40.281 --> 12:42.849
in Pod Bay 1 are dead.

12:42.849 --> 12:44.981
It all falls to us now.

12:44.981 --> 12:46.853
The three of us
