12:53.860 --> 12:55.731
Each of you specialize

12:55.731 --> 12:57.907
in different aspects
of this ship.

12:57.907 --> 13:02.303
I have the most working
knowledge of all of the ship.

13:02.303 --> 13:05.175
When we get past this,
you can elect whomever you like
to be in command.

13:05.175 --> 13:07.874
I have no ambition
