13:15.098 --> 13:17.187
There are only 150 of us left.

13:17.187 --> 13:18.710
Therefore,
our limited food supply

13:18.710 --> 13:22.105
should last us
three times longer.

13:22.105 --> 13:24.325
More than that with rationing.

13:26.022 --> 13:29.983
This ship
