13:45.346 --> 13:47.261
because you'’re the smartest
people in your fields.

13:49.263 --> 13:51.787
We have some of the most gifted
and skilled craftsmen,

13:51.787 --> 13:55.095
brilliant engineers
and scientists,

13:55.095 --> 14:00.317
chosen to build
a colony from scratch
on an alien planet,

14:00.317 --> 14:02.276
to save mankind.

14:05.801 --> 14:09.326
To save our families
back home.

14:13.156 --> 14:15.376
Starting today,

14:15.376 --> 14:18.161
