of this mission.

14:44.709 --> 14:47.843
As we remember
these kind souls,

14:47.843 --> 14:51.194
let us not lose ourselves
in grief.

14:51.194 --> 14:55.633
Instead, let us celebrate
the lives that these...

14:55.633 --> 14:58.114
Saw you try to save
Commander Ingram when
everything went to hell.

14:58.114 --> 15:00.943
Aw, she was a right pill,
that one.

15:00.943 --> 15:04.860
- You guys we close, huh?
- Susan handpicked me for this.

15:04.860 --> 15:10.431
She changed my life.
She saved my life.

15:10.431 --> 15:13.434
I get why the three
lowest ranking lieutenants

15:13.434 --> 15:17.742
were put in the pod bays
with the rest of us peasants,

15:17.742 --> 15:20.093
but why would they put
Ingram in with us?

15:20.093 --> 15:21.398
Strange, right?

15:24.097 --> 15:27.404
...those born
with an exceptional drive
to make this universe

15:27.404 --> 15:29.798
