for the rest of us.

15:29.798 --> 15:33.236
And like the rest of us,
they left the comfort...

15:33.236 --> 15:35.891
That was very impressive
last night.

15:35.891 --> 15:40.678
A little presumptive,
but very take charge.

15:40.678 --> 15:44.987
Perhaps you didn'’t need
